  m_Name: Day 0 Daughter Messages
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08a894b9b170bd4408c3738b6b563b07, type: 2}
  lines:
  - "Hi Dad! Sorry I\u2019m not home today, I\u2019m having to stay away for the
    night for my university placements."
  - Getting hands on experience working at the orphanage is so much fun though!
  - "Putting a smile on everyone\u2019s face is the best feeling, so it\u2019s not
    all bad. Albeit a bit lonely\u2026"
  - "But I hope work is going well for you, and I\u2019m always thankful for how
    much you support me."
  - "And just know that for all the effort you put in, I\u2019m doing my best to
    put twice as much in."
  - Have a good night, see you tomorrow!
